snippet.title: Densha de GO! 2 Kōsoku-hen (PS1)
snippet.description:
Here is a quick gameplay video of 電車でGO！2 高速編 for the Playstation 1. I think that the PS1 version is superior to the PC port by Unbalance because of the cool opening video and the extra sound effects and vocal announcements. The only downer are the horrible graphics (It might just be the emulator). For that, I prefer the PC port's visuals.

Running on OS X Mavericks using OpenEmu.
